<subSubSection id="CD10A6286E79A6162DBC972550D703A6" pageId="0" pageNumber="51" type="description">
<paragraph id="94D08D4852B2AAD94DD689596CE784BF" pageId="0" pageNumber="51">Description of specimens from China.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0BCBBE750A6FFFA2C0354F1A61F226D0" pageId="0" pageNumber="51">
Main description according to an original tail adult specimen (SYS r002573, Fig. 
<figureCitation id="C0E99AFE29E7D68EA6164B67BBB23E65" captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figure 2. A. The general aspect of the adult male specimen of Lygosoma siamense (SYS r 002573) from Sanya, Hainan, China in life; B. Scalation and coloration characters of the head of the same individual." figureDoi="10.3897/herpetozoa.35.e80151.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/654720" pageId="0" pageNumber="51">2</figureCitation>
